Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Intro}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}Sakurai Shinichi started working for us \Npart-time last year.{I'd like to add apostrphe : Shin'ichi -aria}{## how necessary would it be? Might also look off for a name?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thuggish looks aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}he treats his work very seriously, and our regulars \Nhave nothing but good things to say about him.{## might have to yeet the part about having a "serious" personality, which is also kinda implied here anyway?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, most importantly of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an5\pos(1389.9765625,950)}he's got some \Nmighty fine collarbones.{ugh the line here is so plain, work your magic pls light}{## What exactly is she referring to? checked a scanlation, and they say collarbone}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Whoopsie-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an3}He's sure got the stuff.{That Sakurai's something, all right.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon closer inspection, he's pretty hunky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}He looks nice and slender, \Nbut he's actually pretty buff!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai, we'd like to settle the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,On my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}I doubt he's noticed yet, \Nbut he's been attracting a lot of fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You're pretty tall, Sakurai! \NHow many centimetres?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One-eighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you play any sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be in the swimming club.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Swimming team, hip-hip hooray! \NYou've got a detective's hunch, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And while swimming, {\i0}everything{\i1} is laid bare...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}With all these little tidbits \NI'm picking up during work,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd say that's progress ahoy, baby!{## okay I might be going a bit too far now lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart doesn't seem to be into it today, Ami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine to get lost in thought sometimes, \Nbut remember that you're on the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to stay on top of things \Nin this line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lose track of all kinds of things \Nif you aren't careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I understand your hobbies, \Nbut focus on work for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go clear those customers' table.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}Dad might seem nice and gentle, \Nbut he's pretty strict with family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}Oh deary me, I can't act like this during work. \NEspecially not when sharing a shift with Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:01:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiya!
Comment: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:29.98,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, you again?{"Heck, you're here again?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have anything better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Right back at ya! but hey, \Nprops to you for working on a Sunday!{"props to you working on a sunday"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's this? Who? Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad knows her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Up top! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he's just playing along with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Our peak hour's just ended, \Nso you can sit wherever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thanksies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:04:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You mean Uzaki? \NShe's a sophomore at our college.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, she's in college?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, Sakurai! I brought that game you lent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool. What's your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}They're lending out each other's stuff. \NThey must be pretty good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, that final act was a real thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a stand-alone title at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}but when I found out it's actually \Na sequel to some older game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I got {\i1}crazy{\i0} goosebumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I would've been plenty happy \Nif it were a plain ol' building game,{the moment when the game is probably nyancraft -aria}{## ... now I want edit that in}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}but when it turned out to be such a gem, \NI knew I had to get it out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to be getting along pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's with the chuckle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Oh, it's nothing. \NBring her some water, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we go to the same college, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Asai Ami. I'm in my senior year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Then that makes you Sakurai's senior!{goodluck with that light -aria}{## then that makes you Sakurai's Sakurai!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Be right back. I'm gonna stick this \Nin my bag real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Uzaki Hana, and I'm a sophomore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}Now that I've taken a closer look at her, \Nthis girl's an absolute cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's got such a friendly smile...{endearing suits here but just giving context, literally "easy-going", but sometimes used for animals ahahahahha - aria}{## this work?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}She's pretty small, too. \NAlmost like a cute little animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Christ on a bike, that part {\i0}ain't{\i1} like a little animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This girl's no li'l critter—she's an absolute beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no, you gotta pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You two seem to get along really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Oh, yeah, we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you known each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in the same club in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The water on Uzaki's table \Nis getting pretty low.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}He's {\i1}always{\i0} been that gloomy kid \Nin the back of class everyone avoids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting to know him was no easy feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}He's not much different even now, \Nalways one block away from Loner's Lane!{"he has a tendecy to step on the loners' path quickly"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I figured I'd look out for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:05:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, call me over when \Nyou're ready to order, Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's showing real promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to stick your nose in their business,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But you also feel you shouldn't interfere...{you might add to beginning :"also feeling like"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They just make you want to watch over them.{"It's kinda urging to look out for them"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you love customer-facing jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You get to watch all kinds of people \Nand how they live their lives, like these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the thrills of this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzaki. Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}co-o-old{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you bump into me for?!{"why the heck you bump into me"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to ask {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You're a customer! You're supposed to \Nleave waiting to us waiters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}What's this nonsense? You don't even \Ntreat me like a customer half the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They put on quite a show, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:07:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}You're telling me. \NLooks like I'll be taking more shifts soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, give them a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai's out with a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He called this morning. \NI made him take the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}First the ice-water drenching incident, \Nfollowed by a very cold night straight after...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, huh. So much for the "I lift, bro" look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's surprisingly fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah—I lift, bro. {## meme but so good}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why's she still all chipper?{"Actually, why doesn't she have a cold?" then feels so off. }{## how's this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I have been knocked down {\i1}flat{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember colds hitting quite {\i1}this{\i0} hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I go to a doctor? Get some medicine?{"Should I visit hospital? Or maybe I should just take a medicine before thinking that?", the sentence is so long on my version but detailed the context for you, that's why - aria }
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably best if I eat something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What a racket. Who's there? Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And with me barely managing to get out of bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All you really out flat with a cold? \NWell, I'm paying you a visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What... how did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Sakurai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, uh... Sakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be one bad cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like I let her into my place after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, who told her where I live?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}Since I now know where he lives, \NI figured we'd play games or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now {\i0}that's{\i1} some misplaced excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:09:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He looks like he's having a really bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}That cold must be really rough if it's \Ngot him down like that despite his stamina.{woah this one is so wrong lol, "Seeing him, who actually brags about his stamina, lying in his bed shows how bad the cold is."}{## oh damn, that's very different ye}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No... can't really move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Got any medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Didn't think to get any before.{you can add at the end: "after all"}{## assuming he's talking about getting medicine before getting sick}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you haven't eaten either then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. Leave lunch to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Based on his symptoms, I'd say it's probs this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A cold—that calls for leeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you sit up, Sakurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then eat a little, even if it's only a few bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been busting my ass off, I'll have you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Empty fridge, awkward kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Say "ah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can feed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly... I can't really taste anything right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it's probably good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Probably", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See? My cooking is totally edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating really warmed me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a good sweat going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Wipe yourself down and change your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That sweat? It {\i1}stinks{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's fine! I'm just going to \Ntake my medicine and go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! No fighting back, sickie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got nice skin, mister. I'll be gentle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop the weird roleplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget feeling self-conscious, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be used to being \Nhalf-naked from swim club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do the front myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How can being cared for be so tiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Here's your medicine. Take this \Nand you'll be all better in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}But if you're still feeling awful tomorrow, \Nmake sure you see a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go home. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, once you're asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'll chuck the key back in through \Nthe mail slot, so you can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just play games in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already laid low, so let me just say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a huge help today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. That's just how we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai! Sakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I beat this bald scissors dude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}His shields explode \Nwhen I hit 'em with my blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Look, I'll lend you the game {\i1}and{\i0} the console, \Nso just go home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go home a {\i1}loser{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let me {\i1}sleep{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:13.93,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your cold all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks. Sorry you had to cover my shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it. I was free anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't take I take one of your shifts, then? \NI've gotta thank you one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to thank me... \NWould you mind inviting Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, a toast to Sakurai's recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Celebrating my recovery with Korean barbecue... \NThis'll lay heavy on my stomach. {## lmk if I'm overediting this}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:14:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}C'mon! It's all-you-can-eat, \Nand I'm the grill girl, so eat up, Sakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Salted tongue! Chuck! Tripe! Skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you're piling on too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Short ribs! Knuckle! Ribeye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So full of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's happy as a clam now that Sakurai's all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Look at you two knock 'em back! \NAre beer and liquor really {\i1}that{\i0} tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, especially with good food on your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go drinking one day once you're twenty, Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that sorted, eat up, Sakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now. Listen. Here! {## work your magic, Pik}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hit up the ladies' room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're feeling better, Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that I had to take the day off yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just happy Hana took such good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really {\i1}did{\i0} tell her my address...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How did {\i1}what{\i0} go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Please don't pressure me by piling \Nmy plate with the finest cuts of meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, it's not like that between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to enjoy a quiet solo life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}so I'd rather not have to \Nentertain guests if I can help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And Uzaki is the antithesis of "quiet".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Way gloomy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what {\i1}you{\i0} are, Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They've been drinking themselves silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Uzaki may be my trusted junior, \Nbut she's still a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It'd cause nothing but unnecessary trouble for her \Nif rumour spread of her coming to my place often. {## gonna need rewording likely}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I live near campus, \Nand you never know who's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-This is getting complicated!{"Making this complicated!"}{## works fine}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had an inkling, but this? This is dreadful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet he's so attentive of her! Overbearingly attentive!{I'm of two minds on this one but I think it should be " And you so damn conscious when it's about her", like, getting embarrassed and stuff}{## how's this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}Right. It'd be best if we didn't \Npluck this one until it has ripened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}It's like coffee, Ami. \NRoasted slowly, painstakingly brewed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}Let's bide our time and \Ncontinue watching over these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes—until we reach that rich, deep flavour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha all chatting 'bout?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we were discussing work for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}A shipmeant of beans and other \Nheavy packages will be arriving,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}so do you think you can \Ncome in a bit early, Sakurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Ami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Thanks! It'll help a lot to have \Nanother pair of muscles around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sure, but what was that just now \Nbetween you and your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Just psyching ourselves up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Psyching up, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What's up, Uzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you call Ami by her first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If I use her last name, \Nshe'll get mixed up with her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, uh, I was really careful grilling that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, uh... Uzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mhm! Perfect with a side of rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why the hell would Uzaki want to meet me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}She's been acting weird ever since \Nwe went out for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I piss her off somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes on this five-yen coin.
Comment: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TL Note: 5 yen is worth a little over 2 Philippine Peso
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting sleepy, {\i1}very{\i0} sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hypnosis? The hell is she tryna pull?{"now what's she trying to pull fooling around like this"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You will do anything I say, anything I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}I dunno what she's trying to accomplish, but I guess \NI do owe her for taking care of me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever. Guess I'll play along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I sure am feeling sleepy all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Score! Simple people really {\i1}are{\i0} \Nthe easiest to hypnotize!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are you calling "simple", you bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, Sakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we go. I just hope it's nothing unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me by my first name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'd hypnotise me for something {\i0}this{\i1} trivial?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's waiting for it. Guess I'll have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha... Ha... Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha... Hani.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hano.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you messing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Couple of love-dummies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Love-dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Love-dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's the stuff. I'm satisfied for now.{og line: So that's how it works. \NI'm pretty happy with it!}{## can I get a double-TLC-check on this? sounds off to me. I assume she's just happy that her hypnosis worked?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Man, that went better than expected. \NI might be a natural at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if that's all it takes to cheer her up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay! Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Next"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have you buy me a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And ice cream from the convenience store!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can have you buy me lunch at the dining hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\move(960,1024,960,1146.667,2516,2600)}Oh! And you can buy me the latest VR setup, too—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(960,960,960,1005.334,1,60)}Don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5\frz45\fsp4\pos(281.165,702.111)}O{*\frz40.8}u{*\frz36.6}c{*\frz32.4}h{*\frz28.2}!{\frz24} {## pls motion track this kudaplease, mocha hates me}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Faking your hypnosis is dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Says the girl making demands through hypnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You call Ami by her first name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I've known you for a pretty long time, \Nyet all I get is a "Hey" and a "Listen up here".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda rude, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I see. I hadn't realised that \Nwhat I was doing was upsetting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise for that. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}But I'm kind of, uh... uncomfortable \Ncalling girls by their first names.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ami's forced it onto me for work, \Nso I've been trying, but...{I'm doing my best to do what she want me to do and call Ami with her name, because it's related to work " nuance is, ami told her to call her ami, he couldn't refuse cuz it was his work so he needed to}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just anything but that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}That's fine, then. I wouldn't want to force \Na misery guts like you to do my bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Still, hypnotizing with a \Nfive-yen coin in this day and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't think that'd {\i1}actually{\i0} work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Guh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It worked! Are you kidding me?! \NYou must have zero resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Buh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I reverse this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta cover that somewhere in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzaki is flying through the sky.{I'll be flying in the sky}{## This might be one of those very few moments where I think talking about yourself in the third person might not sound awful lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working.
Comment: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:01.90,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Outro}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}told{\i0} you: I wasn't hypnotised!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's legit scary that you can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It didn't happen, okay? \NRather, I'd be impressed if it did!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have an attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad... could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Word goes that hypnosis doesn't work \Non people who don't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means these two...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly appears that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not tell them. It's too amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had an attitude, it'd be a travesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.61,0:23:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You bloody {\i1}suck{\i0} at this!
